24
00:01:57,149 --&gt; 00:02:00,801
in order to avoid the serious toxic reaction as far as possible.

25
00:02:01,081 --&gt; 00:02:09,928
For example, it was mentioned that if the poison was used to treat disease, we should start from Panicum miliaceum

26
00:02:10,254 --&gt; 00:02:16,618
and stop taking as long as the disease is cured and try not to increase its dosage and the increase and decrease of the dosage should be limited.

27
00:02:17,088 --&gt; 00:02:19,384
So it is a progressive increase

28
00:02:19,660 --&gt; 00:02:24,250
