41
00:03:17,000 --&gt; 00:03:20,275
So it is not difficult to understand from the deviation of medicine,

42
00:03:20,555 --&gt; 00:03:24,632
the excessive use of a particular kind of medicine which has a certain deviation will definitely cause toxic reaction.

43 
00:03:24,863 --&gt; 00:03:28,748
In this sense, toxicity and effectiveness are related.

44
00:03:29,031 --&gt; 00:03:31,600
So the treating process using Chinese Traditional Medicine is in fact 

45
00:03:31,835 --&gt; 00:03:34,878
a process of correcting the disorder in the patients by using the deviation of the medicine.

46
00:03:35,159 --&gt; 00:03:40,588
Yes. To make it easier: the principle of treating diseases using Chinese Traditional Medicine is using deviation to correct deviation

47
00:03:40,868 --&gt; 00:03:44,894
and how to understand the saying &quot;cure a poisoned patient with poison&quot;?

48
